text: Babies is a 2020 American documentary web television series. The premise revolves around 15 families around the world during the first year of the life of their babies. ==Episodes== == Release == Part 1 of Babies was released on February 21, 2020, on Netflix. Part 2 was released on June 19, 2020. == References == ==External links== * * * Category:2020 American television series debuts Category:2020s American documentary television series Category:English-language television shows Category:Netflix original documentary television series
